sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Streamlit<br/>:8501
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>:8000 /diagnose
    participant Agent as LangChain<br/>agent (create_agent)
    participant LLM as Ollama<br/>Llama 3.1 8B
    participant Embed as MiniLM
    participant DB as Oracle 26ai
    participant HNSW as HNSW index

    User->>UI: types query, clicks Diagnose
    UI->>API: POST /diagnose {query}
    API->>Agent: diagnose(query)

    Agent->>LLM: system_prompt + 4 tool schemas<br/>+ user query
    LLM-->>Agent: tool_call: find_similar_incidents_filtered<br/>{svc, region, category}

    Agent->>Embed: encode(query)
    Embed-->>Agent: 384-dim query vector

    Agent->>DB: SELECT … VECTOR_DISTANCE(embedding, :v, COSINE)<br/>WHERE service_name=:s AND region=:r …
    DB->>HNSW: graph traversal for top-K
    HNSW-->>DB: candidate row IDs
    DB-->>Agent: top-5 incidents (JSON)

    Agent->>LLM: ToolMessage(incidents)
    LLM-->>Agent: tool_call: get_runbooks_for_incident<br/>{incident_id: 108}

    Agent->>DB: SELECT … runbooks JOIN incident_runbooks<br/>WHERE incident_id=108 (no vector)
    DB-->>Agent: 2 latency runbooks

    Agent->>LLM: ToolMessage(runbooks)
    LLM-->>Agent: tool_call: get_service_owner<br/>{service_name: "payment-service"}

    Agent->>DB: SELECT … FROM services<br/>WHERE service_name=:s (pure relational)
    DB-->>Agent: owner row

    Agent->>LLM: ToolMessage(owner)
    LLM-->>Agent: final assistant message<br/>(synthesized answer)

    Agent-->>API: {answer, tool_calls, tool_results}
    API-->>UI: JSON response
    UI->>User: Answer + Tool calls + Incidents +<br/>Runbooks + Owner panels
